- EnterpriseAuditMiddleware.serialize_simple (method) — invoked in test_serialize_fields; expected to accept an object and update_fields and return a dict of serialized field values (here returning {"is_active": True}).
- Event and EventAction — used to query emitted audit events and assert action types (MODEL_CREATED, MODEL_UPDATED, MODEL_DELETED).
- sanitize_item (function) — used in expected create diff values for date/time fields.
- create_test_admin_user (function) — used to produce authenticated test users.
- generate_id (function) — used to produce unique strings for test data.

